1
00:00:04,080 --> 00:00:05,679
[Previously]
Then we'll join forces and shatter it together.

2
00:00:05,880 --> 00:00:07,959
This secret art that devours divine power.

3
00:00:08,040 --> 00:00:08,919
How long do you think
you can last?

4
00:00:08,920 --> 00:00:09,920
How long do you think
you can last?

5
00:00:09,960 --> 00:00:12,319
An endless stream of heaven and earth power
is converging on him.

6
00:00:12,480 --> 00:00:13,559
It's that young miss of the Ji family.

7
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:14,679
She possesses the Origin Spirit Body.

8
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:16,919
The Extreme Dao is awakening.

9
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:18,839
We have nothing to fear from you!

10
00:00:18,920 --> 00:00:20,679
At worst, we'll sink the entire Central Province!

11
00:00:21,040 --> 00:00:22,759
What he believes in...

12
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:24,639
I believe the same.

13
00:00:24,920 --> 00:00:26,039
The opportunity has come.

14
00:00:26,240 --> 00:00:28,319
Let me test the power
of the Soldier Character Secret!

15
00:00:29,080 --> 00:00:30,080
Go!

16
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:44,679
Heaven's will is manifest.

17
00:00:44,680 --> 00:00:45,919
Ten thousand spirits offer their blood.

18
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:47,039
Protect our Holy Cult!

19
00:00:47,640 --> 00:00:49,039
Earth's mandate stretches eternal.

20
00:00:49,040 --> 00:00:50,239
Ten thousand laws return to one.

21
00:00:50,720 --> 00:00:51,999
May the teachings flourish forever!

22
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:01,280
Master.

23
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:03,199
I was wounded by Ye Fan...

24
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:05,959
The Nine Li Diagram struck my foundation.

25
00:01:06,720 --> 00:01:08,439
Though my injuries have healed...

26
00:01:08,440 --> 00:01:09,759
my lifespan...

27
00:01:10,440 --> 00:01:12,159
has grown even shorter.

28
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:13,200
Master.

29
00:01:13,320 --> 00:01:15,319
Let us go kill that Ye Fan scoundrel for you.

30
00:01:16,520 --> 00:01:18,799
None of you are his match.

31
00:01:19,360 --> 00:01:21,479
There is no need for further pointless sacrifice.

32
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:24,000
You...

33
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:26,799
will inherit my mantle.

34
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:28,560
Master...

35
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:30,559
Your master is about to fall.

36
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:32,559
But the Dao lineage of our sect must not perish.

37
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:35,119
I have already made arrangements with the Wang family of the Northern Desolate Lands.

38
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:36,279
Today...

39
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:38,999
I shall use this broken body to slay the Sacred Body.

40
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,719
The Northern Emperor has promised...

41
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:44,359
to help you all continue the Yin-Yang Dao lineage.

42
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:58,399
Another line of northern wild geese flies south.

43
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,680
Old friends...

44
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:02,879
Without all of you by my side...

45
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,519
it feels like something is missing.

46
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,519
That's enough.

47
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,399
Who are you performing for?

48
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:15,079
What terrible taste.

49
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:17,239
Just burn these broken remains.

50
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,039
Erecting a tombstone is too inauspicious.

51
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:18,959
You've all consumed divine fruits...

52
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,119
and been reborn anew.

53
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,399
But we should still pay our respects.

54
00:02:23,040 --> 00:02:24,599
Why didn't he make one for himself?

55
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,520
Wait...

56
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:29,319
Surviving under six Imperial Weapons this time...

57
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,520
was only possible thanks to all of you.

58
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,519
This Dreamlike Divine Marrow...

59
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:33,399
Everyone...

60
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,680
should share it together.

61
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:38,359
This is truly a priceless treasure.

62
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:39,319
Ye Fan...

63
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:39,879
Thank you.

64
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:41,839
We caused such a huge commotion outside...

65
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:44,039
We should go home and report to our grandfathers.

66
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,279
Until we meet again.

67
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:46,960
Alright.

68
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:48,919
Goodbye, you old bandits!

69
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,680
What about you, young miss?

70
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:54,479
With your brother making such a scene...

71
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,759
you can still stroll back into the Ji family without a care.

72
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:58,639
Now you know how powerful this little immortal is, right?

73
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,639
But I'm not going back yet.

74
00:03:00,880 --> 00:03:01,880
Besides...

75
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:03,160
Without me...

76
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,240
who's going to protect you?

77
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:06,479
So, what's our next move?

78
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:08,079
Do you have any further plans?

79
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,120
After this battle...

80
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:12,720
our fame...

81
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,839
should have spread across the entire Central Province.

82
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:16,919
Trying to keep a low profile...

83
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:17,920
is no longer possible.

84
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,119
We might as well head straight to the Singular Scholar Mansion.

85
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:22,319
Continue investigating clues about the Starry Sky Ancient Path.

86
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:23,959
You're going to the Singular Scholar Mansion too?

87
00:03:24,440 --> 00:03:25,279
Then...

88
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,359
We'll meet again at the Singular Scholar Mansion.

89
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,439
He truly is an ancient saint from Earth.

90
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,360
Could it be...

91
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:42,119
that only by reaching their level of cultivation...

92
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,519
can one embark on the journey home?

93
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,519
You damn scoundrel Ye!

94
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:47,039
You actually dare show up at the Singular Scholar Mansion!

95
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:48,679
Surround him and take him down!

96
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:51,799
This girl...

97
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,519
Isn't she the younger sister of the Southern Demon, Qi Lin?

98
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,479
Don't tell me you and her...

99
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:57,600
It's a long story.

100
00:03:59,320 --> 00:04:00,320
Little Qi.

101
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:02,559
I'm here for my own reasons.
It has nothing to do with you.

102
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:04,479
Can you not be so enthusiastic?

103
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:06,040
You...

104
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,399
You're not leaving here today.

105
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:11,079
Fighting inside the Singular Scholar Mansion
isn't a good look.

106
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,240
Little Ye Zi.

107
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:15,519
You're really not doing a great job
as a follower.

108
00:04:15,720 --> 00:04:17,119
Everywhere you go,
people gather to watch.

109
00:04:18,080 --> 00:04:19,599
Who's watching him?

110
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:21,679
Hey!

111
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:23,719
Since when did I become your follower?

112
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:25,559
I'm the one leading you around...

113
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,439
searching everywhere for that Starry Sky Ancient Path.

114
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:27,359
I wasn't even finished speaking.

115
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:28,599
Yet here you are,
following right behind me.

116
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,039
Do you people even take me seriously?!

117
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:30,839
This works too?

118
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:34,159
You're really going too far!

119
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:38,039
One flower, one world.

120
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:44,279
Qi Qi!

121
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:45,079
Come back!

122
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,240
Let go of me!

123
00:04:47,440 --> 00:04:49,999
Today, no matter what,
I must kill him!

124
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:51,640
You all should disperse as well.

125
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,160
Withdraw!

126
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,199
Nine Dragons Pulling a Coffin.

127
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,519
Ancient Desolate Forbidden Land.

128
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:07,879
I've seen you before.

129
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:13,520
Brother Ye.

130
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,399
Why don't we step aside and talk?

131
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:21,679
You dozen or so people crossed the star domain...

132
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:23,559
and emerged from the Ancient Desolate Forbidden Land.

133
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:25,999
You scattered across the Eastern Wastelands.

134
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,239
You...

135
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,839
are one of them.

136
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,120
How did you know?

137
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,919
My Southern Demon Emperor Hall's Blood Sacrifice Altar...

138
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:35,839
possesses a treasure

139
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:37,119
called the Heaven and Earth Dharma Eye.

140
00:05:37,960 --> 00:05:38,799
This treasure...

141
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:40,079
can cross vast distances...

142
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:41,519
and peer into the heavens and earth.

143
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,279
Since ancient times...

144
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:45,519
there have been many legends of visitors from beyond the domain.

145
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,639
I never imagined...

146
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:49,559
I would witness one with my own eyes.

147
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,560
In that case...

148
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:52,959
I won't hide anything either.

149
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:56,079
Brother Qi's family lineage is ancient and profound.

150
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,440
I wonder...

151
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:59,679
if you possess any method to reach beyond the domain?

152
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:03,400
Regrettably...

153
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:05,120
I do not know either.

154
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:08,199
But every time I gaze at the starry sky...

155
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:09,759
I can't help but imagine...

156
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,759
what the world on the other side of the stars looks like.

157
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:14,599
That place is ancient and distant.

158
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:16,599
Though it is my homeland...

159
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:19,159
there are still many unknown ancient histories.

160
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:21,719
Even I know nothing about them.

161
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,559
To never set foot in that world...

162
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:25,879
would ultimately be nothing but an empty dream.

163
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:28,279
Brother Ye...

164
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,480
Could you tell me more about the world beyond the domain?

165
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:32,879
Could you describe it to me?

166
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:39,999
Since Brother Ye has treated me with sincerity...

167
00:06:40,320 --> 00:06:41,679
when our paths cross on the Imperial Road one day...

168
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,680
if you are defeated...

169
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:43,919
I will let you leave.

170
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:45,639
Consider it repayment for today's kindness.

171
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,000
Take care.

172
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,320
Ye Fan...

173
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:58,599
I didn't expect you and the Southern Demon
to get along so well.

174
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:00,759
But...

175
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:01,119
But...

176
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,759
What exactly did you two talk about?

177
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:05,319
Why is it that every time your homeland comes up...

178
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:06,919
you always become so mysterious?

179
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,799
Even the big guy starts acting strange.

180
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:11,999
Ye Fan...

181
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:14,999
The grudge between us...

182
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,639
Today...

183
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:21,599
it must be settled once and for all.

184
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,600
Step aside!

185
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,000
Ye Fan!

186
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:32,439
My Yin-Yang Cult has stood in the Central Province for ten thousand years.

187
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:33,799
Our Dao lineage continues unbroken.

188
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:36,679
You have repeatedly killed our Holy Sons and Holy Maidens...

189
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,999
and sought to sever our inheritance.

190
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:40,519
Today, I cannot let you live.

191
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,959
Do you have some kind of persecution complex?

192
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,120
Those Holy Sons and Holy Maidens of yours...

193
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:46,079
weren't they all stolen genius seedlings from other sects?

194
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:48,079
You call that a pure inheritance?

195
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:49,079
Shut your mouth!

196
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:51,319
My lifespan is running out, and time waits for no one.

197
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:53,319
Today, I will eliminate you for the sake of future generations.

198
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,320
You really think...

199
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:56,759
this is enough to kill me?

200
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:14,920
Old thief!

201
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:16,959
Your Yin-Yang Cult cannot tell right from wrong...

202
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,159
and twists the truth.

203
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,039
You should have been struck down by heaven long ago!

204
00:08:20,063 --> 00:08:48,463
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

205
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,119
Cowardly turtle!

206
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:52,280
Come out and face me!

207
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:04,039
Wang Yangzhan was heavily wounded
by the Nine Li Diagram.

208
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:05,479
His combat strength is far from before.

209
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,679
Burning his lifespan like this
to power the treasure...

210
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:09,719
He won't be able to hold on much longer.

211
00:09:11,680 --> 00:09:13,079
You're already at your limit.

212
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:15,239
Now accept your death!

213
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:42,879
I've got you!

214
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,440
Little brat...

215
00:09:55,760 --> 00:09:57,479
I know how cunning you are.

216
00:09:57,800 --> 00:10:00,519
But all I need is one look at you
from this distance...

217
00:10:00,680 --> 00:10:02,279
and the curse will strike you for sure.

218
00:10:02,680 --> 00:10:04,919
I have already formed an alliance with the Northern Emperor.

219
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:06,679
In exchange for the life of the Sacred Body...

220
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:09,119
my Yin-Yang Cult shall enjoy another era of glory.

221
00:10:09,520 --> 00:10:11,919
I will not have died in vain.

222
00:10:20,800 --> 00:10:22,159
It's too late.

223
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:25,679
This is my Yin-Yang Cult's Yin-Yang Death Curse.

224
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:27,079
There is no cure in this world.

225
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,440
Ye Fan...

226
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,559
Using this broken body as the medium...

227
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:37,999
I burn the last of my lifespan to cast the Yin-Yang Death Curse.

228
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:41,039
Even if my soul scatters into oblivion...

229
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:44,119
I will drag you down to the Yellow Springs with me!

230
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:48,039
Yin-Yang Death Curse!

231
00:10:58,760 --> 00:10:59,359
Ye Zi...

232
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:00,720
Don't come any closer!

233
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:07,919
Ye Fan...

234
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,240
Ye Zi...

235
00:11:16,800 --> 00:11:17,800
Ye Zi...

236
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:31,959
I've been hit by that old bastard's
Yin-Yang Death Curse.

237
00:11:42,800 --> 00:11:45,079
Even my divine phenomenon can barely resist it.

238
00:12:06,760 --> 00:12:07,760
This is bad.

239
00:12:07,800 --> 00:12:08,800
The death curse...

240
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:10,159
is rushing toward my sea of consciousness.

241
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:11,599
It wants to destroy my divine sense.

242
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:14,239
If my divine sense is destroyed...

243
00:12:14,680 --> 00:12:15,759
everything is over.

244
00:12:16,040 --> 00:12:17,239
The Yin-Yang Death Curse...

245
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:18,240
burns all things...

246
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:19,399
and destroys all spirits.

247
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:20,719
Do not approach this barrier...

248
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:22,959
lest the curse's flames spread to you.

249
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:24,079
Elder...

250
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,239
Is there any way to break this death curse?

251
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:26,559
The Singular Scholar Mansion's library is vast.

252
00:12:26,560 --> 00:12:28,159
There must be a method to dispel it.

253
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:33,959
The Sacred Body commands countless secret arts.

254
00:12:34,560 --> 00:12:36,359
If he reached the Saint Lord realm...

255
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:38,199
he would be nearly unmatched in the world.

256
00:12:38,760 --> 00:12:41,279
Breaking the Yin-Yang Death Curse would be no problem.

257
00:12:41,880 --> 00:12:44,759
But right now, his cultivation is still too low.

258
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:45,919
Judging by this situation...

259
00:12:46,040 --> 00:12:47,919
he can only last a day and a night at most.

260
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:49,639
This person...

261
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:50,679
doesn't have long to live.

262
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,000
Ye Zi...

263
00:12:54,040 --> 00:12:55,359
You can definitely hold on.

264
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,399
I'll stay right here and watch over you.

265
00:12:58,160 --> 00:12:59,999
If anyone dares speak rudely...

266
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:01,519
or harbors ill intentions...

267
00:13:01,920 --> 00:13:03,359
I'll be the first to cut them down!

268
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,519
Ye Fan, hold on!

269
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:50,279
It's useless, Zi Yue.

270
00:13:50,800 --> 00:13:52,199
Stop wasting your energy.

271
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,039
Young Miss...

272
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:04,279
What are you doing?

273
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:07,159
This is the ring from the Bronze Immortal Palace.

274
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:10,279
It might be able to break the death curse.

275
00:14:10,280 --> 00:14:12,159
This secret treasure has fused with your primordial spirit.

276
00:14:12,280 --> 00:14:13,319
You cannot summon it lightly...

277
00:14:13,320 --> 00:14:14,439
nor can you destroy it.

278
00:14:14,680 --> 00:14:15,719
Otherwise you will fall.

279
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:16,959
Using it recklessly now...

280
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:19,199
will surely bring great disaster.

281
00:14:20,640 --> 00:14:22,279
This secret treasure comes from the Immortal Domain.

282
00:14:22,920 --> 00:14:24,079
Its power is impossible to fully predict.

283
00:14:28,680 --> 00:14:30,239
Perhaps it's worth the risk.

284
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:32,079
Ji Ziyue...

285
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:33,280
Don't go over there!

286
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:51,159
Ye Fan...

287
00:14:51,160 --> 00:14:52,160
Zi Yue...

288
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:53,559
Don't come any closer!

289
00:14:56,280 --> 00:14:57,280
Young Miss...

290
00:15:08,880 --> 00:15:10,399
I won't just watch you die.

291
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:29,359
Even if I have to exhaust every treasure I possess...

292
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:31,079
I will save you.

293
00:15:33,712 --> 00:15:35,712
[Mini Lecture on Heavenly Knowledge]

294
00:15:36,562 --> 00:16:01,896
[Yin-Yang Death Curse: The ultimate strike used by generations of Yin-Yang Sect leaders at the brink of death. Once unleashed, whether king or ruler, none can escape. The caster kills the enemy—but must also sacrifice themselves, enduring endless torment and refinement before death. This is a curse formed from a lifetime of slaughter. When the death curse is activated, it destroys everything—leaving no solution.]

295
00:16:01,920 --> 00:16:37,920
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

